arcconf - Command line interface to configure PMC-Sierra
(Microsemi) Controllers.

arcconf_migration.py.data covers arcconf functionality 
specific to Migration and Rebuilding functionality.
 
Note:
    1. supported controllers pci_ids can be entered 
       separated by space " "
    2. ensure to set spare_drive only if rebuild
       functionality need to be tested. 
    3. Specify only one initial raid level i.e 
       initial_raid in yaml file per yaml iteration. 
